2763const struct Property *
2764CSSPropertyNamesHash::findPropertyImpl (register const char *str, register unsigned int len)
2765{
2766 if (len <= MAX_WORD_LENGTH && len >= MIN_WORD_LENGTH)
2767 {
2768 unsigned int key = propery_hash_function (str, len);
2769
2770 if (key <= MAX_HASH_VALUE)
2771 {
2772 register int index = lookup[key];
2773
2774 if (index >= 0)
2775 {
2776 register const char *s = property_wordlist[index].name;
2777
2778 if (*str == *s && !strncmp (str + 1, s + 1, len - 1) && s[len] == '\0')
2779 return &property_wordlist[index];
2780 }
2781 }
2782 }
2783 return 0;
2784}

2864const char* getPropertyName(CSSPropertyID id)
2865{
2866 if (id < firstCSSProperty)
2867 return 0;
2868 int index = id - firstCSSProperty;
2869 if (index >= numCSSProperties)
2870 return 0;
2871 return propertyNameStrings[index];
2872}
2873
2874const AtomString& getPropertyNameAtomString(CSSPropertyID id)
2875{
2876 if (id < firstCSSProperty)
2877 return nullAtom();
2878 int index = id - firstCSSProperty;
2879 if (index >= numCSSProperties)
2880 return nullAtom();
2881
2882 static AtomString* propertyStrings = new AtomString[numCSSProperties]; // Intentionally never destroyed.
2883 AtomString& propertyString = propertyStrings[index];
2884 if (propertyString.isNull()) {
2885 const char* propertyName = propertyNameStrings[index];
2886 propertyString = AtomString(propertyName, strlen(propertyName), AtomString::ConstructFromLiteral);
2887 }
2888 return propertyString;
2889}

2891String getPropertyNameString(CSSPropertyID id)
2892{
2893 // We share the StringImpl with the AtomStrings.
2894 return getPropertyNameAtomString(id).string();
2895}
2896
2897String getJSPropertyName(CSSPropertyID id)
2898{
2899 char result[maxCSSPropertyNameLength + 1];
2900 const char* cssPropertyName = getPropertyName(id);
2901 const char* propertyNamePointer = cssPropertyName;
2902 if (!propertyNamePointer)
2903 return emptyString();
2904
2905 char* resultPointer = result;
2906 while (char character = *propertyNamePointer++) {
2907 if (character == '-') {
2908 char nextCharacter = *propertyNamePointer++;
2909 if (!nextCharacter)
2910 break;
2911 character = (propertyNamePointer - 2 != cssPropertyName) ? toASCIIUpper(nextCharacter) : nextCharacter;
2912 }
2913 *resultPointer++ = character;
2914 }
2915 *resultPointer = '\0';
2916 return WTF::String(result);

3415
3416bool CSSProperty::isInheritedProperty(CSSPropertyID id)
3417{
3418 ASSERT(id <= lastCSSProperty);
3419 ASSERT(id != CSSPropertyInvalid);
3420 return isInheritedPropertyTable[id];
3421}
3422
3423CSSPropertyID getRelatedPropertyId(CSSPropertyID id)
3424{
3425 switch (id) {
3426 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyTextOrientation:
3427 return CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyWebkitTextOrientation;
3428 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyWebkitTextOrientation:
3429 return CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyTextOrientation;
3430 default:
3431 return CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyInvalid;
3432 }
3433}

4168 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyHeight:
4169 switch (id2) {
4170 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyInlineSize:
4171 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyBlockSize:
4172 return true;
4173 default:
4174 return false;
4175 }
4176 default:
4177 return false;
4178 }
4179}

4373
4374bool CSSProperty::isDescriptorOnly(CSSPropertyID id)
4375{
4376 switch (id) {
4377 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyAdditiveSymbols:
4378 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyFallback:
4379 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyFontDisplay:
4380 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyNegative:
4381 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyPad:
4382 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyPrefix:
4383 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyRange:
4384 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertySrc:
4385 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertySuffix:
4386 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertySymbols:
4387 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertySystem:
4388 case CSSPropertyID::CSSPropertyUnicodeRange:
4389 return true;
4390 default:
4391 return false;
4392 }
4393}
